    <url>/2019/11/11/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p>
<h2 id="1-新建文章"><a href="#1-新建文章" class="headerlink" title="1. 新建文章"></a>1. 新建文章</h2><p>先打开git-bash，在git-bash中进行操作</p>
<p>新建：</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new "文章题目"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>文章头部添加信息：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: hexo搭建博客常用命令</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-11-11 14:54:46</span><br><span class="line">tags: </span><br><span class="line">- hexo</span><br><span class="line">- github</span><br><span class="line">- blog</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- hexo</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="2-部署脚本"><a href="#2-部署脚本" class="headerlink" title="2. 部署脚本"></a>2. 部署脚本</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy # 部署到github</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
